:null,"euaPriceEUR":null,"euaVerified":null,"euaEstimated":null,"euaPurchased":null,"euaBalance":null}},{"portName":"Tuxpan","displayOrder":3,"co2":121.502599999999990000,"eeoi":15.697002239551262000,"aer":11.302793497730418000,"soxMt":0.357000000000000000,"sox":0.046121069010208840,"noxMt":3.890000000000000000,"nox":0.502551704340931100,"euEtsDetails":{"allowancePurchases":null,"eua":0.000000000000000000,"euaCostUSD":null,"euaCostEUR":null,"euaPriceUSD":null,"euaPriceEUR":null,"euaVerified":null,"euaEstimated":null,"euaPurchased":null,"euaBalance":null}}]},"remarkList":[{"modifiedDate":"2024-08-28T11:23:49.797","modifiedByFull":"Heng, Rainer","remark":"included COFR expenses usd 566.25"},{"modifiedDate":"2024-02-09T18:16:33.61","modifiedByFull":"Fitzgerald, Ethan","remark":"The Dee4 Juniper was set to load Houston and discharge in Pajaritos. After arriving in Pajaritos and waiting for almost 18 days, PMI sent revised orders to discharge in Tuxpan followed by Veracruz. There was no cargo discharged in Pajaritos, so we called this an interim port and will bill all time, costs, and bunkers as well as the deviation in a lumpsum of $972,779. Tuxpan was an additional port billed at $63k in freight.\n\nAlong with the long waiting time in Pajaritos which was billed in the lumpsum, we also had 14 days in Veracruz. Total demurrage was $830k over 16 total days. Bunker consumption increased due to the extended time in port as well as two ports added so more passage time. Port costs also increased dur to the added port, however the costs were covered in the lumpsum for Tuxpan.\n\nOverall, the main differences are due to the demurrage/waiting time in Mexico. Operations ran smoothly with Dee4."},{"modifiedDate":"2024-01-29T15:02:44.727","modifiedByFull":"Land, Macy","remark":"Had to remove an invoice with preliminary dem which was showing an additional 2 days of dem."},{"modifiedDate":"2024-01-24T14:37:41.623","modifiedByFull":"Land, Macy","remark":"CVE and Urea consumption included."},{"modifiedDate":"2024-01-23T19:59:58.333","modifiedByFull":"Land, Macy","remark":"Vsl should depart 2 days earlier. Removed demurrage and additional berth."},{"modifiedDate":"2024-01-22T16:22:11.423","modifiedByFull":"Land, Macy","remark":"Additional berths in Tuxpan and Veracruz."},{"modifiedDate":"2024-01-22T16:09:58.61","modifiedByFull":"Land, Macy","remark":"Additional days in Veracruz. Only added 1 dem. day as weather has been poor during stay which is 50%."},{"modifiedDate":"2024-01-17T20:38:58.09","modifiedByFull":"Land, Macy","remark":"Expected to sail 3 days sooner."},{"modifiedDate":"2024-01-08T17:36:59.307","modifiedByFull":"Land, Macy","remark":"Updated VMS based on the est deviation costs and time"},{"modifiedDate":"2024-01-08T14:26:40.897","modifiedByFull":"Land, Macy","remark":"No cargo disch in Pajaritos. Sailed to Tuxpan. Extended stay in Veracruz (estimated)"},{"modifiedDate":"2024-01-02T16:53:07.863","modifiedByFull":"Land, Macy","remark":"Veracruz will be interim port (out of Geo). Included a lumpsum to cover port costs, time, bunkers for deviation and time in port."},{"modifiedDate":"2024-01-02T14:23:00.35","modifiedByFull":"Lin, Zackary","remark":"more waiting days at Pajaritos"},{"modifiedDate":"2023-12-27T14:35:58.42","modifiedByFull":"Lin, Zackary","remark":"more waiting days at pajaritos"},{"modifiedDate":"2023-12-27T11:15:53.98","modifiedByFull":"Dragheim, Carsten Bo","remark":"CVE 01/01-01/02 (USD 2k)"},{"modifiedDate":"2023-12-19T15:50:13.063","modifiedByFull":"Land, Macy","remark":"Additional port which carol included the l/s. Adding in the port here, port costs, and demurrage."},{"modifiedDate":"2023-12-18T20:38:48.433","modifiedByFull":"Land, Macy","remark":"21k of bunkers saved on laden passage"},{"modifiedDate":"2023-12-18T15:57:14.453","modifiedByFull":"Land, Macy","remark":"Extended time in Pajaritos (estimated)"},{"modifiedDate":"2023-12-15T14:26:46","modifiedByFull":"Land, Macy","remark":"Extended time in Hou. Demurrage u